  {
    "_id": "5a7d6ab82542aa2b05a42394",
    "_layout": "right",
    "_type": "component",
    "_parentId": "5a7d6ab42542aa2b05a42393",
    "body": "<p>The second session looked at the promise of big data and how Google Flu Trends became the poster child for big data and then its biggest failure. This session was used to highlight the dangers of relying just on &#39;Big Data&#39;.&nbsp;</p><p>We also highlight the risks of not being able to deal with the 4 V&#39;s of big data. If you can&#39;t manage any of the 4 V&#39;s then it should send warning signs!</p><p>The University of Washington has a fantastic series of lectures on this topic <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X0XqnAqvyIk&amp;index=25&amp;list=PLPnZfvKID1Sje5jWxt-4CSZD7bUI4gSPS\" target=\"_blank\">available on youtube</a>.</p>",
    "displayTitle": "The big data hubris",
    "title": "The big data hubris",
    "_isAvailable": true,
    "_isOptional": false,
    "_classes": "",
    "_component": "text",
    "instruction": ""
  },
  {
    "_id": "5a7d6c4a2542aa2b05a42397",
    "_layout": "left",
    "_type": "component",
    "_parentId": "5a7d6c432542aa2b05a42396",
    "body": "<p>It is critical to consider the ethical implications carefully when using data to inform decision making.&nbsp;</p><p>The <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/524298/Data_science_ethics_framework_v1.0_for_publication__1_.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Data science ethical framework</a> paper from the cabinet office contains many&nbsp;examples of good and bad use of data to inform decision making and build services.</p><p>Additionally the Open Data Institute has developed the <a href=\"https://theodi.org/the-data-ethics-canvas\" target=\"_blank\">data ethics canvas</a>,&nbsp;designed to help identify potential ethical issues associated with a data project or activity.&nbsp;</p>",
    "displayTitle": "Data ethics",
    "title": "Data ethics",
    "_isAvailable": true,
    "_isOptional": false,
    "_classes": "",
    "_component": "text",
    "instruction": ""
  },
