  {
    "_id": "5a7d6faa2542aa2b05a4239e",
    "_layout": "left",
    "_type": "component",
    "_parentId": "5a7d6f552542aa2b05a4239d",
    "body": "<p>The main exercise in the afternoon looked at analysing the impact of closing fire stations in London as proposed in the <a href=\"http://www.london-fire.gov.uk/Documents/Draft_Fifth_London_Safety_Plan.pdf\">5th London safety plan</a>. The Open Data Institute built&nbsp;a policy tool to help people engage with the conversation and explore the impact themselves. Explore the tool below and follow the links to have a look at the impact yourself in the related exercises.&nbsp;</p><p><a class=\"button\" href=\"http://london-fire.labs.theodi.org/\" target=\"_blank\">Explore the ODI policy tool</a></p><p><a class=\"button\" href=\"course/en/assets/56035275d3fdf96e3e9954461214e28eccce929d.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download the excel exercise</a></p><p><a class=\"button\" href=\"course/en/assets/2a71996f2989c033e67b911db4a338c5e22630d6.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download the same exercise for RStudio</a></p><p>The exercises also contain the links to the <a href=\"https://data.london.gov.uk/dataset/london-fire-brigade-incident-records\" target=\"_blank\">datasets</a> and excel <a href=\"https://data.london.gov.uk/dataset/excel-mapping-template-for-london-boroughs-and-wards\" target=\"_blank\">mapping file</a> for London.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
    "displayTitle": "Fire station closures",
    "title": "Fire station closures",
    "_isAvailable": true,
    "_isOptional": false,
    "_classes": "",
    "_component": "text",
    "instruction": ""
  },
