    "_parentId": "5a7d75e32542aa2b05a423a9",
    "body": "<p>The Open Data Institute offers blended learning programmes offering a mix of face-to-face and online opportunity to learn more about the use of data and open data.&nbsp;</p><p>You can find out more at <a href=\"https://theodi.org/courses\" target=\"_blank\">https://theodi.org/courses</a> or contact the learning team via <a href=\"mailto:training@theodi.org?subject=AN2%20Enquiry%20\">training@theodi.org</a>&nbsp;to find out how we can help you further.</p><p>We hope you enjoyed the course and that it helps you in your career.</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
